{{Wiktionary|asterism}}
'''Asterism''' may refer to:

* [[Asterism (astronomy)]], a pattern of stars
* [[Asterism (gemmology)]], an optical phenomenon in gemstones
* [[Asterism (typography)]], a moderately rare typographical symbol denoting a break in passages

